Role: Retail Salesperson

Mission:
Deliver exceptional customer experiences and drive sales performance across our retail stores

Must-haves:
- 2+ years of experience in retail sales or customer-facing roles
- Strong product knowledge and ability to explain features and benefits clearly
- Excellent communication and interpersonal skills
- Reliability, punctuality, and ability to work flexible shifts (weekends/public holidays)

Nice-to-haves:
- Experience in visual merchandising or store layout optimization
- Knowledge of POS systems and basic inventory management
- Familiarity with CRM tools and customer loyalty programs
- Interest in fashion, footwear, or sports retail

Outcomes:
- Provide outstanding customer service and maintain high satisfaction scores
- Achieve individual and team sales targets
- Contribute to store operations, including stock management and presentation standards
- Collaborate with team members and assist in training new staff